00:05:48,144 --> 00:06:16,767
on top of that you're making gifts you actually you know do something more than just make people happy you actually offer them things so it's to relatives and guests ancestors so that's to the that's making some sort of remember in those days you made sacrifice for the benefit of others often it was animal sacrifice you know the great king's sacrifice was I believe hundreds of horses and cows and

