82
00:13:16,818 --> 00:13:32,000
So, the Blessed One sent to the householder anatapindika, so it's the same person, there are householders these four kinds of happinesses, which may be achieved by a layperson who enjoys sensual pleasures depending on time and occasion.

83
00:13:32,881 --> 00:13:33,363
What for?

84
00:13:33,442 --> 00:13:36,226
The happiness of possession, the happiness of enjoyment,

85
00:13:36,645 --> 00:13:40,110
The happiness of freedom from debt and the happiness of blamelessness.

86
00:13:40,770 --> 00:13:42,432
So these are the happinesses.

87
00:13:42,893 --> 00:13:47,359
But the first one you notice is to do with sensual pleasure.

88
00:13:47,619 --> 00:13:50,381
So what is the happiness of possession?

89
00:13:50,682 --> 00:13:57,410
Here a family man possesses wealth acquired by energetic striving and so on.

90
00:13:57,990 --> 00:14:04,458
And when he thinks I possess wealth acquired in this way, righteously gained, he experiences happiness and joy.

91
00:14:05,164 --> 00:14:06,846
This is the happiness of possession.

92
00:14:09,269 --> 00:14:11,770
And then what is the happiness of enjoyment?

93
00:14:12,652 --> 00:14:21,360
So with the wealth acquired by energetic striving and so on, a family man enjoys his wealth and does meritorious deeds.

94
00:14:21,419 --> 00:14:27,004
All these two always come together, to enjoy your wealth and to do meritorious deeds.

95
00:14:27,024 --> 00:14:32,049
And he thinks with the wealth acquired in this way, I enjoy my wealth and do meritorious deeds.

96
00:14:32,570 --> 00:14:34,312
and he experiences happiness and joy.

97
00:14:34,371 --> 00:14:37,716
This is called the happiness of enjoyment.

98
00:14:37,735 --> 00:14:40,298
And what householder is the happiness of freedom from debt?

99
00:14:41,059 --> 00:14:45,644
Here a family man is not indebted to anyone to any degree, whether small or great.

100
00:14:46,066 --> 00:14:52,653
And when he thinks, I'm not indebted to anyone to any degree, whether small or great, he experiences happiness and joy.

101
00:14:53,193 --> 00:14:58,620
This is called the happiness of freedom from debt.

102
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:01,563
And what householder is the happiness of blamelessness?

103
00:15:02,083 --> 00:15:08,412
Here, householder, a noble disciple is endowed with blameless conduct of body, speech and mind.

104
00:15:08,591 --> 00:15:15,942
And when he thinks, I am endowed with blameless conduct of body, speech and mind, he experiences happiness and joy.

105
00:15:16,081 --> 00:15:18,024
And this is the happiness of blamelessness.

106
00:15:18,846 --> 00:15:28,597
These, householder, are the four kinds of happiness that a lay person who enjoys sensual pleasures may enjoy depending on time and on occasions.

107
00:15:30,772 --> 00:15:45,205
I can only hope these words have been of some assistance and that you will continue to enjoy your life and do meritorious deeds and in such a way arrive at that lovely place sooner rather than later.

108
00:15:51,811 --> 00:15:52,532
Very good.

